data.name: ABOUT_lblAboutDescription_Text
data.value: Conga X-Author for Excel intelligently interacts between Microsoft Excel, Chatter, and Salesforce using embedded configurable ribbons. The technology allows all tasks performed within a Microsoft Excel Document to be shared and completely captured in any Structured Data System including Salesforce, without the need to go into Salesforce or Chatter.
